description: Testing standards — Vitest, component tests, service tests, edge cases
globs: src/**/__tests__/**/*.test.{ts,tsx}

## Testing Rules
1. Vitest with @testing-library/react for components
2. Test service layer (mock fetch/storage)
3. Test store layer (Zustand)
4. Test UI components (render, interaction, states)
5. Each test file covers: happy path, edge cases, error states
6. No test depends on another test (isolated)
7. beforeEach clears state
8. Mock external dependencies (Gemini API, fetch)
9. Test file name matches source: [source].test.ts
